{
  "stem": "7093.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, to tell about my brother, I have to tell what happened to the men.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Hungary, all of the men at the age of 18 had to go into the army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The men could not go into the army-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I mean, the Jewish men went into the army, but were not given arms, but were taken into mines and road-building and very, very hard work in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and they were not taken only at the military age, but they were taken up to the age of 50.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Which meant that we had no men who were around between 18 and 50.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All the men were taken away or practically all of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were one or two, but, I mean, there were for some reasons there were exceptions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But most of the men were away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of the sergeants amused himself and threw down stones on them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And therefore, he had a finger injured to the-- to the extent that he had to relearn his technique later on completely, because this one finger was completely out of action.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he never really made it-- really quite made it and most probably that was the main reason.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- the group with which he was, and most of the groups of the Hungarian men, were eventually taken out into the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, they were taken around about July, August.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that summer, the summer of '44, was an incredibly hot summer, which I will come back to a number of times.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was an incredibly hot summer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were taken with all their clothing and all their belongings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they marched and were given very little food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And therefore, they eventually discarded most of their luggage, most of their belongings.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
